descriptions: I like to make things on the web. I currently lead the development team at Modern Message. I also make and produce music and stories. I live in the Lakewood neighborhood of Dallas, Texas. I have previously lived in Pennsylvania, Arizona, Florida, Virginia and Bosnia. I am permanently in love with Carissa Byers.
